 的受访者认为「不应该推进」，高于认为「应该推进」的 37%。民调结果还显示，越年轻的受访者，越赞成推进「上四休三」制度；年收入越高的受访者，越支持推进「上四休三」，其中年收入在 800 万日元（约合 37 万元人民币）以上的群体中，有 51% 认为「应该推进」，而年收入不足 800 万日元的群体中，则只有 34% 的受访者认为「应该推进」。英媒：东京都政府计划明年 4 月启动「上四休三」工作制，以扭转日本低出生率"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b450a201ff1e1ba663d59d3007a078e7_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6979349938"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIr7mS8brQsod8EAMaCTExMjM3MjY1NiCYhv66BjAAOLwBQApyCjY5NzkzNDk5Mzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1734352299.233697", "card_id": "Q_657610089", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 232}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么很多二游和动漫都对「永远活在美梦里」呈批判与反对的态度？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "很可笑的是，反对「活在梦里」的主角本身就是作者意识投射和活在梦里没什么区别 。如果让这些主角得知自己和反对的反派一样近乎于活在梦中，他们是否会原地自戕？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a0ff6712dd6577631526b573294cfefa_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657610089"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIr7mS8brQsod8EAMaCTEwODQxMzQzOCD6zt6yBjAAOOECQAtyCTY1NzYxMDA4OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1734352299.234010", "card_id": "Q_6423876623", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 43}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "阅读《西游记》最大的收获是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2016ef85987d0927d9c5126a35a09bac_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度",