图的时间基本能对应，法院认定加班事实存在。法院认为，用人单位违法解除劳动关系的，应向劳动者支付赔偿金 32411 元，加班费 18135.2 元。 （参考来源：领导点赞下属加班的朋友圈！公司赔了 1.8 万！）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-005fc36b8d815710ad441cd439cc95c5_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6571845691"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIr7mS8brQsod8EAMaCTExMjI5MTAwMCCT/uS6BjAAOKkBQA5yCjY1NzE4NDU2OTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1734352299.235283", "card_id": "Q_6211986834", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价「暗黑系」游戏《流放之路 2》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "现在开始封测了，大家感觉怎么样"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-087fbaf615bfa7eee2f18f4eeae1e4db_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6211986834"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIr7mS8brQsod8EAMaCTExMjIxOTIwNyDW6c+6BjAAOCdAD3IKNjIxMTk4NjgzNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1734352299.235582", "card_id": "Q_6980602034", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "韩国执政党党首韩东勋辞职，会带来哪些影响？国民力量党在韩国政坛还能保持竞争力吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "韩国执政党国民力量党党首韩东勋 16 日举行记者会，表示辞去党首职务。新华社分享页"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-17e6885247f3ee4adfa863db210c3ac4_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6980602034"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIr7mS8brQsod8EAMaCTExMjM3